{"text_id":187887,"tokens":["When"," making"," important"," decisions"," or"," facing"," challenges"," in"," life",","," seeking"," advice"," from"," others"," can"," be"," invaluable","."," While"," one"," opinion"," can"," provide"," new"," insights"," and"," perspectives",","," seeking"," multiple"," opinions"," can"," be"," even"," more"," beneficial","."," Here","'","s"," why",":","\n\n","Diversity"," of"," Thought",":"," Different"," people"," have"," varying"," backgrounds",","," experiences",","," and"," ways"," of"," thinking","."," When"," you"," seek"," advice"," from"," multiple"," individuals",","," you"," introduce"," a"," diversity"," of"," thought"," to"," your"," decision","-","making"," process","."," This"," can"," help"," you"," understand"," the"," issue"," from"," different"," angles"," and"," uncover"," creative"," solutions"," that"," you"," might"," not"," have"," considered"," otherwise","."," It"," prevents"," you"," from"," sticking"," to"," a"," single"," perspective"," and"," encourages"," you"," to"," approach"," the"," problem"," hol","istically",".","\n\n","Comple","mentary"," Skills"," and"," Knowledge",":"," Each"," person"," has"," their"," own"," set"," of"," skills",","," expertise",","," and"," life"," experiences","."," By"," seeking"," opinions"," from"," individuals"," with"," different"," strengths",","," you"," can"," benefit"," from"," their"," specialized"," knowledge","."," For"," example",","," if"," you","'","re"," faced"," with"," a"," career"," decision",","," chatting"," with"," a"," career"," counselor"," can"," provide"," insight"," into"," your"," options"," and"," what"," steps"," to"," take",","," whereas"," speaking"," to"," a"," person"," who"," is"," successful"," in"," the"," field"," you","'","re"," interested"," in"," can"," give"," you"," a"," realistic"," picture"," of"," that"," profession","."," Multiple"," opinions"," enable"," you"," to"," leverage"," the"," expertise"," of"," different"," individuals",","," making"," your"," decision"," more"," informed",".","\n\n","Objec","tivity"," and"," Confidence",":"," When"," you"," seek"," advice"," from"," multiple"," individuals",","," you"," increase"," the"," likelihood"," of"," receiving"," objective"," opinions"," unaffected"," by"," personal"," biases","."," This"," is"," particularly"," important"," when"," the"," decision"," involves"," emotions"," or"," subjective"," elements","."," By"," hearing"," similar"," feedback"," from"," various"," sources",","," you"," can"," build"," confidence"," in"," your"," decision",","," knowing"," that"," multiple"," independent"," individuals"," share"," the"," same"," assessment"," or"," suggestion","."," ","\n\n","Wider"," Perspective"," on"," Risks"," and"," Benefits",":"," Different"," people"," may"," highlight"," different"," risks"," or"," benefits"," associated"," with"," a"," particular"," choice","."," Understanding"," these"," varying"," perspectives"," can"," help"," you"," gauge"," the"," potential"," downsides"," and"," ups","ides"," more"," thoroughly",","," allowing"," you"," to"," make"," a"," more"," informed"," decision"," about"," the"," potential"," consequences","."," ","\n\n","In"," my"," personal"," experience",","," seeking"," multiple"," opinions"," has"," been"," invaluable","."," When"," I"," was"," deciding"," on"," a"," major"," in"," college",","," I"," spoke"," to"," professors",","," advisors",","," and"," professionals"," in"," fields"," that"," interested"," me","."," Their"," varied"," insights"," helped"," me"," understand"," the"," pros"," and"," cons"," of"," each"," choice"," and"," ultimately"," led"," me"," to"," choose"," a"," major"," that"," aligned"," with"," my"," passions"," and"," strengths","."," Had"," I"," solely"," relied"," on"," one"," opinion",","," I"," might"," have"," made"," a"," decision"," based"," on"," limited"," information"," and"," missed"," out"," on"," opportunities",".","\n\n","In"," conclusion",","," s